{"tid":758213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人解釋到點解男人被帽後要係咁同其他人講？","createTime":"2018-07-27T12:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T14:29:38.000Z","uid":77320,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b83fc3bc73aa4a563ddfad971eb779950178f612","tid":758213,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"女派帽俾個男<br />\n然後個男周圍同佢自己圈子既人講<br />\n話條女係臭雞之類<br />\n<br />\n但係其實佢圈子既人係唔識條女<br />\n佢又冇擺條女上facebook連登<br />\n所以對條女既名譽係冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而佢圈子既人都知係因為條仔窮同冇用先會被帽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男人要尊嚴唔係應該收埋唔同人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢咁做同落自己面有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人解釋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2764dc7ba13856347060048761b99d23873c05a4","tid":758213,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"死傷一千 殺敵八百 (佢以為可以)"},{"pid":"8ca004090f5d9590d7d85378a5c254bf674ef067","tid":758213,"uid":161731,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"應該要似啲女被人強姦左之後都要收收埋埋 然後跳樓死左去 啱唔啱呀？"},{"pid":"1a7227596fcdef09291bda908d610e12e4c584a3","tid":758213,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"你肯為左面子而自己屈住屈住咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上唔覺帶綠帽有咩恥辱，唔知自己帶/帶左都唔肯除就真係柒"},{"pid":"41631a6d897ed9b6ed3f63ad0eaf237ae8fcadf6","tid":758213,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:51:57.000Z","msg":"不如問下點解女人帽完人會周圍同人講先"},{"pid":"c23b6a67d732b1932214f70e23e1ac47284bfa3a","tid":758213,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:53:45.000Z","msg":"講漏左<br />\n個男冇朋友既<br />\n身邊既人埋佢身或者佢埋人身只係為左利益/合作<br />\n（不過表面上會扮兄弟）"},{"pid":"c41f2729e3c8ad4a8c9355a2940ed4024b